 1. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the dunhill-smoker##5
 2. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 4. the bolivar-smoker is the australian##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 6. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
 7. the person eating watermelon is somewhere between the dunhill-smoker and the australian##7
 8. the person eating apricot is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the dunhill-smoker##5
10. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the chaman-smoker##5
11. the chinese is the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
