 9. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
10. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
11. the designer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
12. the russian is the owner of the horse##1

